articles.title: Russia makes biggest 24-hour Ukraine advance in over a year
articles.description: Russia has made its most significant advance in Ukraine in over a year [2].

articles.title: Texas shooter who killed 3 outside Target, including a child, randomly chose his victims, police say
articles.description: A shooter in Austin, Texas, killed three people, including a child, outside of a Target store, and police say the victims were chosen randomly [3].
